Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 你在耍我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你…你是指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是不是自己通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:02:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得了A評價就嘲笑我 耍我？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼會…我沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}區區一年級新生 別得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是…要是沒有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就能參加比賽了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然是試音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高年級生落選而低年級生入圍 就決不是什麼稀奇的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}儘管如此 是不是所有人都能老實接受這個結果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這又是另一回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黃前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是…啊 夏紀學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天練習完後能陪我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有話想和你聊 陪我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我請客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那晚點見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:02:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人心複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:08.81,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\blur2\bord1.8\3c&HAA6D5B&\c&HFEFEFE&\pos(710,520)}正直坦率的小號
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}3分25秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指定曲就照剛剛的節奏來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}競賽的演奏時間共12分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然超時顯然是不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是因為心急而搞砸了演奏就更不可取
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請不要忘記剛剛的節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}時間足夠我們演奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼今天就到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝指導
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老師 請問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}單子上寫的這個「毛毯」是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是毛毯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望各位同學能將家裡不用的毛毯借出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我家積了好多毛毯沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是要毛毯做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就敬請期待到時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子 等等告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說你今天有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小綠說她想吃甜食想得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我今天有話要和她聊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黃前就借給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我在樓下等你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笑容有點可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 快改掉這個習慣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這一段總是演奏得不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為是節奏突然轉換的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香織
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我這就過去 等等再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊…嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H827AE2&\be1\pos(870,306)}獨奏試音\N\h\h\h\h一定要吹這裡！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香織學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高坂是小號的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我有聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 說要請客卻只請這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}草莓口味的可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過我是巧克力派的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就算不想喝 也得給我喝就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}試音落選了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 我覺得只是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏紀學姐吹得比我好太多…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對 我剛剛不是在居高臨下嘲諷人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼嘛 你果然很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我吹上低音號本來也就一年而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}試音落選我也不在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我看見學姐練得很認真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼嘛 偷看還不說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過 我會練習是因為現在社團裡的氣氛觸動了我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是說被瀧老師騙上鉤了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我挺容易受別人影響的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但老師全看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他要我吹還沒有練習過的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我便吹得一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以黃前是憑實力贏下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經接受了 甚至覺得這結果真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以就別為我操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那你想聊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我就是想說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你有帶樂譜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 有帶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一開始就想寫給久美子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.43,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&HA0A09E&\pos(206,386)}一定要拿到金獎！我們明年一起吹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.30,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&HA0A09E&\pos(304,464)}一定要拿到金獎！我們明年一起吹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝 多虧了黃前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得我稍微進步了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}稱讚我也得不到什麼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}錢包裡只有點零錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以一定是那個的錯啦 絕對！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎？才不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經接受結果了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老師做出了判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}認為高坂同學比我更能勝任獨奏聲部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是試音吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我說那場試音本身…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}優子也能參加競賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下來大家就應該以金獎為目標來努力 不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幫我將這句話也向其他同學說一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香織學姐 請你不要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是你最後一次的大賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請不要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐…香織學姐絕對要實現自己的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不然的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多出來的就掛到牆上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 原來不是要大家在這過夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想的話就這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過我還是會回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老師 這邊弄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在這個房間內的聲音會被毯子吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}音量會減小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想讓聲音更響亮 就要吹得更大聲更準確
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比賽的禮堂要比這個教室大上幾十倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了讓演奏響徹禮堂 平時就要注意這點來練習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那各位開始練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老師 我可以問個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瀧老師以前就認識高坂麗奈 是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要問這個問題呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}優子 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有傳言說老師在試音中偏袒了她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請回答我是不是 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我絕沒有偏袒 或是特別對待某位同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全員的評審都是公平公正的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那您和高坂同學很早就認識了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的父親交情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以在她國中時期 我就認識她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您為什麼瞞著不說？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我覺得沒有說出來的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會因此在指導上做出改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請不要再侮辱老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道我是為什麼會被選上的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我就是吹得比香織學姐還好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你自以為是也要有個限度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}優子 別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你以為香織學姐放了多少心在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想挑毛病就先練到比我好再說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請繼續準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們開始練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗奈 麗奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}煩死了 煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是受夠了 那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:56.90,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吹得那麼差 還有臉說那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不這麼覺得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你笑什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我還以為你肯定會很消沉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你覺得我有錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我不覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我爸爸是職業的小號演奏家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瀧老師的父親則是個有名的管樂老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以兩個人才會認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我也認識瀧老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瀧老師會來這所學校的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我好不容易才從媽媽那裡聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以就拒絕了保送
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的假的 嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我喜歡瀧老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是「Like」的那種喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:11:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而是「Love」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Love？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你別再複誦了 羞死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是瀧老師不知道我的這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他絕對不會在試音中偏袒我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她居然在這個時候說顧問老師的壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你那什麼臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼 就是覺得麗奈好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}個性真差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有想過讓出獨奏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有 我要讓她們認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這都做不到 還怎麼當獨特的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這才像你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過或許那時我們還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要堅強下去 要當特別的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會是多麼困難的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:54.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(236,72)}上低音號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:54.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&HBDA40F&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(229,67)}上低音號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:12:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算沒有偏心的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對認識的還是會有差別待遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有人說其實這次試音就是為了讓高坂同學能在大賽獨奏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高坂同學的父親是個挺有名的小號演奏家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那老師肯定很難拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}懷疑在同學心中不斷膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瀧老師卻依然保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣看來反而像要掩蓋問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}社員們的懷疑更深了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種氣氛就沒辦法改變一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小綠是想要高坂讓出獨奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得這可能也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高坂同學沒做錯什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小綠我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 與其鬧得這麼僵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子是怎麼想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:55.56,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H6F7A7B&\fs25\blur4\t(0,2000,1\blur0)\move(594,214,590,268,0,5494)}師\N生\N面\N談\N中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畢竟是關係到高坂同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說是師生面談
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但現在還是一年級的第一學期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高中生活感覺怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼大問題 也交了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼將來想做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就好好讀書吧 特別是數學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有社團活動上別因為一些雜事而分心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好好為大賽做準備 享受音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我上囉 我上囉～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 別鬧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼都在收拾了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我們不是在收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為大家說太熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以練習開始前就先…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可沒說過能把毯子收起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請放回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放回去 現在開始動作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鐮屋燕同學 有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結果今天還是分聲部練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在這個狀態太難合奏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 法國號和單簧管他們完全無法集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為心裡全是懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聲部長會議上 社長好像反覆勸了很多遍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是大家看起來都無法相信老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}照這樣下去再拿個銅獎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我和加藤試音落選就沒意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是社長已經盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那明日香學姐的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對啊 明日香學姐應該能說服大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這可難說啊 她這個人比較特別
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過都關係到大賽了 情況就不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子 能幫我們問問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 我來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果是你的話 明日香學姐就會開口的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我大概能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香學姐對待黃前的感覺有點不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺很認同你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}確實可能如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上吧 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺他們把麻煩都丟給我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香織學姐…是獨奏聲部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在偷看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嚇到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:17:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧是黃前 嗅出好地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼嗅出來啊…只是剛好走過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結果她還是沒有就此放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香織學姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她不是對試音有所不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}更別說別人的同情 她完全沒冀求過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是自己無法接受這個結果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接受？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 她想要讓自己接受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香學姐是怎麼想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}試音的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香織學姐和麗奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你覺得哪個比較適合吹獨奏段落？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這我可無法回答你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我好歹是個副社長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}個人想法無可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那只在這裡告訴我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香學姐的個人想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黃前果然很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能保密嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盡我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老實說 我心底覺得根本無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰來獨奏這問題太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這究竟是真心話還是場面話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香學姐的面具實在太厚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算我想瞭解她的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卻也對這層面具無計可施
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黃前同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}社長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香學姐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概是回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這只能靠自己了 晴香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比賽快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}音樂真是美好的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你無法說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好聽就只能稱讚好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我記得你父親也說過這話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 我想老師很快就要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但在這之前我有話跟大家說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:55.76,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我想啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瞳同學認真聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最近到處都是針對老師無憑無據的流言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}導致大家的集中力都分散了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比賽之前鬧成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣下去別說金獎 我覺得銀獎都很難說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}儘管他認識部分學生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也不能說明他會在試音中偏袒誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果還是有所不滿的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也不要在背後偷偷說壞話了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請現在舉起手來 我會傳達給老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不滿試音結果的人請舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天還真安靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要舉手？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舉手的是不滿試音結果的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}優子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天我有件事要先通知大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:21:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有跟大家說過吧 下週會借場地進行練習
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}借此機會我想花點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對有意願的人進行二次試音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對上次試音結果有意見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想要再試一次的同學現在請舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下週再在所有人面前演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會根據大家舉手的結果決定是否合格
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家一起作出決定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣就沒有意見了吧 可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼請問
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想參與二次試音的同學請舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請讓我再參加一次獨奏聲部的試音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香織…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼你和暫定的獨奏人選 高坂同學兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}針對誰更適合獨奏 進行二次試音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接著 下一樂章奏響了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.96,0:22:09.99,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord0.5\pos(1080,570)} 待續
